div.head:
{@sūcīpatra
gadā paboṅg
biṣaẏa pr̥ṣṭhāṅka@}

lg.head:
{@goḷayuddha prabeśa o yoginīgaṇagkara
duryyodhanara raktanadī santaraṇa o
bhīṣṁaṅka sahita mantraṇā@}

div.head:
{@duryodhanara hastinā prabeśa,
byāsa sarobara gamane rāṇī bhānumatī
o pitā mātāṅka saha parāmarśa@}

lg.head:
{@dakṣa yajña
o
byāsa sarobarara bibaraṇa@}

{@bhīmaṅka sahita duryyodhanara gadā yuddha
o
bhīmaṅkara kṣīra samudre patana@}

{@diryyodhana urubhaṅgak, baḷarāmaṅka prabeśa
yudhiṣṭhiraṅkara śoka o
dvārakā gamana@}
